  "remarks": "National identification no: a) Indonesia National Identity Card 3573010405480001 b) Indonesia National Identity Card 353010405480001. Acting emir of Jemmah Anshorut Tauhid (JAT) (QE.J.133.12.). Associated with Abu Bakar Ba’asyir (QI.B.217.06), Abdul Rahim Ba’aysir (QI.B.293.11) and Jemaah Islamiyah (QE.J.92.02). Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 15 November 2021.; Listing: Listed by UN 1989 Committee on 12 March 2012 (amended on 27 May 2022)",
